888
00:54:21,613 --> 00:54:22,614
HAENGBOK PAWNSHOP

889
00:54:24,908 --> 00:54:27,911
[Woogy breathing heavily]

890
00:54:28,829 --> 00:54:30,038
Dammit.

891
00:54:30,414 --> 00:54:32,207
[grunts]

892
00:54:32,291 --> 00:54:33,500
You motherfucker.

893
00:54:33,584 --> 00:54:35,419
[groans]

894
00:54:37,921 --> 00:54:39,298
The fuck.

895
00:54:44,761 --> 00:54:45,971
[gunshot]

896
00:54:47,639 --> 00:54:48,640
[metal clangs]

897
00:54:49,266 --> 00:54:51,393
[exhales]

898
00:54:51,476 --> 00:54:54,479
[♪ dramatic music]

899
00:54:54,563 --> 00:54:57,566
[Dokyung breathing heavily]

900
00:55:35,020 --> 00:55:38,023
[♪ music continues]

901
00:56:12,057 --> 00:56:15,060
[♪ music continues]

902
